Create SoulFantasy:
1)Basic (random) (0.15 XCH): 
send XCH to adress xch15dhq9av7aujx4u0v33allgn44td7exa8nvyuy7dxftjyg27r40gsyde5uq with memo "@your_nickname receiving_address" 
and make a post mentioning @SoulFantasy8.

2)Special cosplay or other wishes (0.25 XCH):
send XCH to adress xch15dhq9av7aujx4u0v33allgn44td7exa8nvyuy7dxftjyg27r40gsyde5uq with memo "@your_nickname receiving_address your_wishes" 
and make a post mentioning @SoulFantasy8.

Within 24 hours you will receive your SoulFantasy.

If your wishes do not comply with the rules of Chia Network's blockchain or forgot to specify "your_wishes", you will receive a basic SoulFantasy.
If you sent XCH by accident, forgot to specify "@your_nickname" or "receiving_address" or less than the required amount - you will not receive nft.
